title: Kristin Shares Her Awkward Exchange At A Restaurant + DJ Willie T’s Weekly Wrap Rap
description:
It’s been YEARS since we’ve done this, but it’s back by popular demand! Our Show Director Tommy, formerly of the rap group Def Force (true story) brings you what you missed this week, rap style. 
But first, Kristin shares a story with us about an awkward encounter she had at restaurant.
